releaseNotes:
1. In 2-3 times has increased speed of the HTML and XHTML minification, and in 10-15 times speed of the XML minification;
2. In HTML/XHTML settings were added the following three properties: UseShortDoctype, UseMetaCharsetTag and RemoveJsProtocolFromAttributes;
3. In HTML settings the RemoveJsTypeAttributes and RemoveCssTypeAttributes properties now have default values equals to true, because they are now considered is safe;
4. In XML settings was added one new property - the CollapseTagsWithoutContent, and was renamed the RemoveComments property to RemoveXmlComments.
